      • verifySettings

        public boolean verifySettings()
        This method is called every time Apica Git Integration Weblet loads, and checks the remote settings of the repository.match it with the remote from GitConfiguration File.
        Returns:
        if there are no remote it returns false... if user just change protocol, from https to ssh or vice versa, it will update the remote and return true
